    <description>A .NET global tool that wraps the upstream mikefarah/yq YAML/JSON/TOML processor.
      Install once, run anywhere: dotnet tool install -g yq.tool
      This is an unofficial repackaging. All credit goes to Mike Farah (https://github.com/mikefarah/yq).</description>
    <tags>yq yaml json toml tool cli</tags>
